{"tid":1814183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"下一步係要配合美國圍堵中國","createTime":"2020-01-06T21:17:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T01:31:18.000Z","uid":132859,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2faa0402a654901f38d655f22aa0d8d696aed557","tid":1814183,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T21:17:49.000Z","msg":"美國而家當咗中國係冷戰對手<br />\n最驚嘅係<br />\n1. 敏感軍民兩用科技會被中國利用<br />\n2. 中國利用美國資本市場壯大戰略企業<br />\n依兩樣嘢都要利用香港先做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以其實下一步係要<br />\n1. 連登舉報<br />\n香港可以入口好多軍民兩用科技<br />\n反而中國唔得<br />\n所以大家返工嘅時候<br />\n記住睇清楚公司嘅敏感儀器有冇俾人不當咁用 <br />\n有就即刻上嚟篤灰<br />\n幫美國手去搵理由唔再供應敏感儀器俾香港<br />\n<br />\n2. 全部香港人改變投資策略<br />\n中國用香港呢個市場去集資救命<br />\n呢啲集資工具一定會隱瞞好多風險<br />\n所以無論係國債定係國企<br />\n都唔好再買"},{"pid":"bc8f58f66a4481ebeaed81cf8579c42fc039da56","tid":1814183,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T22:59:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90c600138922776419b79b0ed4e1d4081c68b4d","tid":1814183,"uid":133525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T23:13:50.000Z","msg":"收到！"},{"pid":"1c0376f1cdc2ac5090fa335941065d4c414a0937","tid":1814183,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:22:32.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc5d9c33830f96a294f61722d4167aa2e0d5e03","tid":1814183,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:25:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記住睇清楚公司嘅敏感儀器有冇俾人不當咁用 <br />\n有就即刻上嚟篤灰</blockquote><br />\n好似離職之後舉報前公司用翻版咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a3b8c1a823f9893d669d80cd36251a1b2d76e1","tid":1814183,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:27:07.000Z","msg":"其實2點都好易做"},{"pid":"8e15269a92f8d11f449e2536c6eb7baaa6341a82","tid":1814183,"uid":216888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:31:18.000Z","msg":"講下有咩敏感科技例子"}]}